{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban horns in automobiles that only sound when the cars ignition is switched on.",
        "additional_details": "I would like to see the law changed so all car manufacturers are required to make cars that have horns that work at all times, with or without the ignition turned.",
        "background": "If you are a driver or a passenger in a parked car and there is an emergency or you have an accident you cannot always use the horn to alert a possible danger if you don't have the cars ignition switched on. This isn't safe.",
